{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Challenging platformer with drag and jump mechanics controlled entirely with your mouse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206750/extras/gifTundra.gif?t=1735318412\" />Test your temper across four levels, each with unique obstacles and atmosphere. Use your mouse to control direction and strength of the jump. Swing on physics-based chains to overcome greater distances. Avoid every trap designed with only one goal: to kill you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206750/extras/GifOaza.gif?t=1735318412\" />Pick up the potions to get needful lives when you reach the checkpoint. Find out the time and number of deaths it took to finally complete the level, and try to bring those numbers down on your next attempt. Have fun and dont get too mad. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206750/extras/GifyFaily.gif?t=1735318412\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206750/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735318412","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206750/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1735318412","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206750/20436b4188f7bb032c3a70d63c659d7b7fb7b952/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1735318412","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206750/20436b4188f7bb032c3a70d63c659d7b7fb7b952/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1735318412","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Challenging platformer with drag and jump mechanics controlled entirely with your mouse.</p><p class=\"bb_p